Manifest.name: Latitude 5500 - LAB
Manifest.description: Catalogo para Laboratorio Latitude 5500 - Drivers+BIOS - Nivel Critico

Description.Display: This package contains the driver for the Intel AX211, AX210, AX201, AX200, 9560, 9462, 9260, 8265, and 3165 Bluetooth cards. Bluetooth driver is the software that helps your operating system to communicate with Bluetooth devices. This update addresses Common Vulnerabilities and Exposures (CVE). Common Vulnerabilities and Exposures (CVE) is a list of security vulnerabilities and exposures that are publicly disclosed.

Name.Display: Intel HD/UHD/Iris/Iris Pro/Iris Plus Graphics Driver

Description.Display: This package contains the Intel graphics driver for 6th, 7th, 8th, and 10th generation Intel processors. A graphics or video driver is the software that enables communication between the graphics card and the operating system, games, and applications. This update addresses the Intel Security Advisory INTEL-TA-00508 and INTEL-TA-00566. A security advisory is a statement when a security vulnerability impacts a product, and a remedy is available for the vulnerability. The following are the supported graphics cards: Intel HD Graphics 510/520/515/530/520/535/P530/610/615/620/630/P630 Intel UHD Graphics 620/610/630/P630/600/605 Intel Iris Graphics 540/550/555/P555 Intel Iris Pro Graphics 580/P580 Intel Iris Plus Graphics 640/650/645/655

Description.Display: This package contains the Realtek High Definition audio codec. Audio driver is the software that helps your operating system to communicate with audio devices such as internal sound cards, speakers, headsets, and microphones. This update addresses the Intel Security Advisory INTEL-SA-00354. A security advisory is a statement when a security vulnerability impacts a product, and a remedy is available for the vulnerability.

Name.Display: Dell Precision 3540 and Latitude 5400/5500 System BIOS

Description.Display: This package contains the Dell system BIOS update. BIOS is a firmware package that is embedded on a small memory chip on the system board. It controls the keyboard, monitor, disk drives, and other devices. This update addresses Common Vulnerabilities and Exposures (CVE). Common Vulnerabilities and Exposures (CVE) is a list of security vulnerabilities and exposures that are publicly disclosed.

This package contains the driver for the Intel AX211, AX210, AX201, AX200, 9560, 9260, 9462, 8265, and 3165 wireless cards. Wireless drivers help your operating system to communicate with wireless devices such as wireless cards and network interface controllers. This update addresses Common Vulnerabilities and Exposures (CVE). Common Vulnerabilities and Exposures (CVE) is a list of security vulnerabilities and exposures that are publicly disclosed.
